data.description: 3bd 2ba home on almost an acre! Walking distance to coffee shop and stores! Home has space for everyone! Split bedroom arrangement. Large dining space off kitchen with added cabinets and wet bar or could be used as another living space. Large laundry room with extra storage. Another bonus space off of the dining for additional living space or could be used as 4th bedroom! Large level backyard perfect for gardening, grilling and playing ball! New hvac.
